{
  "id": "64db16f3ad3b90001bc9279a",
  "title": "こだわりの意味の変容",
  "created": 1692079861,
  "updated": 1745459883,
  "lines": [
    {
      "id": "64db16f3ad3b90001bc9279a",
      "text": "こだわりの意味の変容",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1692079861,
      "updated": 1692079861
    },
    {
      "id": "6535eb896eb4060000057cd8",
      "text": "[こだわり]",
      "userId": "58442db3ee4a2400116eb406",
      "created": 1698032521,
      "updated": 1698032524
    },
    {
      "id": "64db16f45b98c200004f0261",
      "text": "もともとネガティブな意味だった",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1692079861,
      "updated": 1692079927
    },
    {
      "id": "64db16fb5b98c200004f0262",
      "text": "近年、ポジティブな意味でも使うようになった",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1692079868,
      "updated": 1692079922
    },
    {
      "id": "64db17185b98c200004f0263",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1692079897,
      "updated": 1692079897
    },
    {
      "id": "6535ec695e90c00000b1abc9",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "60508ed36a7abc00235e90c0",
      "created": 1698032745,
      "updated": 1698032756
    },
    {
      "id": "6535ec695e90c00000b1abcb",
      "text": "　「[拘り]」の漢字からすると、もともとはあまりプラスのニュアンスではなさそう[cFQ2f7LRuLYP.icon]",
      "userId": "60508ed36a7abc00235e90c0",
      "created": 1698032745,
      "updated": 1698033047
    },
    {
      "id": "6535ec695e90c00000b1abcc",
      "text": "　　[拘泥]、[拘束]",
      "userId": "60508ed36a7abc00235e90c0",
      "created": 1698032745,
      "updated": 1698032745
    },
    {
      "id": "6535ec695e90c00000b1abcd",
      "text": "　　捕らえて動けないようにするイメージ",
      "userId": "60508ed36a7abc00235e90c0",
      "created": 1698032745,
      "updated": 1698032745
    },
    {
      "id": "6535ecab5e90c00000b1abd0",
      "text": "　和語における「こだわり」の語誌については未調査",
      "userId": "60508ed36a7abc00235e90c0",
      "created": 1698032811,
      "updated": 1698033218
    },
    {
      "id": "6535ecbf5e90c00000b1abd1",
      "text": "　　勘だけど仏教系の方でみかけそう[cFQ2f7LRuLYP.icon]",
      "userId": "60508ed36a7abc00235e90c0",
      "created": 1698032831,
      "updated": 1698033218
    },
    {
      "id": "6535f0315e90c00000b1abd9",
      "text": "　辞書",
      "userId": "60508ed36a7abc00235e90c0",
      "created": 1698033713,
      "updated": 1698033717
    },
    {
      "id": "6535ede35e90c00000b1abd4",
      "text": "　　https://kotobank.jp/word/こだわり-502182#:~:text=こだわり%20こだはり,拘泥(こうでい)%E3%80%82",
      "userId": "60508ed36a7abc00235e90c0",
      "created": 1698033123,
      "updated": 1698033218
    },
    {
      "id": "6535ede45e90c00000b1abd5",
      "text": "　　日国精選版では江戸時代の評判記、[色道大鏡](1678)の用例",
      "userId": "60508ed36a7abc00235e90c0",
      "created": 1698033124,
      "updated": 1698033355
    },
    {
      "id": "6535efb65e90c00000b1abd8",
      "text": "　 　>評判記・色道大鏡（1678）四「もはや御立帰も有まじきに、かく御こだはりありても専なし」",
      "userId": "60508ed36a7abc00235e90c0",
      "created": 1698033590,
      "updated": 1698033603
    },
    {
      "id": "6535ee075e90c00000b1abd6",
      "text": "　　となれば少し前の日葡辞書あたりでも用例が確認できるかもしれない",
      "userId": "60508ed36a7abc00235e90c0",
      "created": 1698033159,
      "updated": 1698033596
    },
    {
      "id": "6535ec695e90c00000b1abce",
      "text": "　微細なことにとらわれて動けない→微細なことに気が及ぶ　みたいな意味の変遷がありそう",
      "userId": "60508ed36a7abc00235e90c0",
      "created": 1698032745,
      "updated": 1698032745
    },
    {
      "id": "6535ec695e90c00000b1abcf",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "60508ed36a7abc00235e90c0",
      "created": 1698032745,
      "updated": 1698032745
    },
    {
      "id": "6809977b00000000006361c4",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "5d69dde930e3c500170f1ffd",
